org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager.containermanager.linux.resources

接口 ResourceHandler

  • 所有已知子接口:
    CpuResourceHandler, DiskResourceHandler, MemoryResourceHandler, OutboundBandwidthResourceHandler
    所有已知实现类:
    CGroupsBlkioResourceHandlerImpl, CGroupsCpuResourceHandlerImpl, CGroupsMemoryResourceHandlerImpl, FpgaResourceHandlerImpl, GpuResourceHandlerImpl, NetworkPacketTaggingHandlerImpl, NumaResourceHandlerImpl, ResourceHandlerChain, TrafficControlBandwidthHandlerImpl

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
 @InterfaceStability.Unstable
public interface ResourceHandler
    Handler interface for resource subsystems' isolation and enforcement. e.g cpu, memory, network, disks etc

    • 方法详细资料

      • bootstrap

        List<PrivilegedOperation> bootstrap(org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configuration configuration)
                             throws ResourceHandlerException
        Bootstrap resource susbsystem.
        返回:
        (possibly empty) list of operations that require elevated privileges
        抛出:
        ResourceHandlerException

      • preStart

        List<PrivilegedOperation> preStart(Container container)
                            throws ResourceHandlerException
        Prepare a resource environment for container launch
        参数:
        container - Container being launched
        返回:
        (possibly empty) list of operations that require elevated privileges e.g a) create a custom cgroup b) add pid for container to tasks file for a cgroup.
        抛出:
        ResourceHandlerException

      • reacquireContainer

        List<PrivilegedOperation> reacquireContainer(org.apache.hadoop.yarn.api.records.ContainerId containerId)
                                      throws ResourceHandlerException
        Require state for container that was already launched
        参数:
        containerId - if of the container being reacquired.
        返回:
        (possibly empty) list of operations that require elevated privileges
        抛出:
        ResourceHandlerException

      • postComplete

        List<PrivilegedOperation> postComplete(org.apache.hadoop.yarn.api.records.ContainerId containerId)
                                throws ResourceHandlerException
        Perform any tasks necessary after container completion
        参数:
        containerId - of the container that was completed.
        返回:
        (possibly empty) list of operations that require elevated privileges
        抛出:
        ResourceHandlerException

      • teardown

        List<PrivilegedOperation> teardown()
                            throws ResourceHandlerException
        Teardown environment for resource subsystem if requested. This method needs to be used with care since it could impact running containers.
        返回:
        (possibly empty) list of operations that require elevated privileges
        抛出:
        ResourceHandlerException
